{"tid":1047609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"靖國神社縱火案周四開審 中國人郭紹傑將自辯","createTime":"2019-03-05T05:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T06:01:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95e66691c5a6c1dc8e61ba4b1d4428311c165ab3","tid":1047609,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"中國人郭紹傑去年12月，趁南京事件81周年到日本靖國神社外焚燒東條英機道具龕牌及展示「毋忘南京大屠殺」標語，郭與同行的社運人士嚴敏華即場遭日本警方拘捕並拘留至今。郭、嚴2人的案件將於本周四（7日）開審，保釣行動委員會表示，得悉2人心情和健康尚好，並已作好自辯的準備。<br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會透露，香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機將明日（6日）專程到東京，他首先會探訪2人，然後擬於本周四到法庭聽審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190305/59332067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59332067&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak7%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=8040ab1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F59332067&h=851a947a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190305/59332067</a>"},{"pid":"97246900da6926ccb234d33ee451c4dd05d66b74","tid":1047609,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"今次嘅重點唔係我有冇縱火 而係浪子回頭金不換"},{"pid":"f5c37f561f57b6ce3e5795dd5656f47530ed92f2","tid":1047609,"uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"97246900da6926ccb234d33ee451c4dd05d66b74","tid":1047609,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"今次嘅重點唔係我有冇縱火 而係浪子回頭金不換"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/181806_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F181806_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=40e71341&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb857dac1800b0b3c7a732d4